<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>FUNCOIN ($FUN) | Just Memes. No Promises.</title>

<style>
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
}

body {
  background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #0b0f1a, #05070d);
  color: white;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Glow effects */
.glow {
  position: absolute;
  width: 400px;
  height: 400px;
  background: #00d9ff;
  filter: blur(150px);
  opacity: 0.2;
  top: -100px;
  left: -100px;
}

.glow2 {
  position: absolute;
  width: 400px;
  height: 400px;
  background: gold;
  filter: blur(180px);
  opacity: 0.15;
  bottom: -100px;
  right: -100px;
}

/* Navbar */
nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 20px 10%;
}

.logo {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: bold;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}

.logo span {
  color: #00d9ff;
}

.btn {
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: 1px solid #00d9ff;
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.btn:hover {
  background: #00d9ff;
  color: black;
}

/* Hero */
.hero {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 100px 20px;
  position: relative;
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: 60px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}

.hero h1 span {
  color: gold;
}

.hero p {
  margin-top: 20px;
  font-size: 18px;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

/* Mascot */
.coin {
  width: 180px;
  height: 180px;
  margin: 40px auto;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f7c948, #caa100);
  box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4);
  position: relative;
  animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.coin::before {
  content: ":)";
  position: absolute;
  top: 55px;
  left: 55px;
  font-size: 50px;
  color: #111;
}

@keyframes float {
  0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
}

/* Section */
.section {
  padding: 80px 10%;
  text-align: center;
}

.cards {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 20px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 40px;
}

.card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  width: 250px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

/* Footer */
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px;
  opacity: 0.6;
  font-size: 14px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="glow"></div>
<div class="glow2"></div>

<nav>
  <div class="logo">FUN<span>COIN</span></div>
  <a class="btn" href="#">Buy $FUN</a>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>FUNCOIN <span>$FUN</span></h1>
  <p>Just a meme. Just a coin. Just vibes.</p>

  <div class="coin"></div>

  <p style="margin-top:20px; opacity:0.7;">
    No promises. No roadmap. No financial advice.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>Why FUNCOIN?</h2>

  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>😂 Meme First</h3>
      <p>Built for internet culture, not finance hype.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>⚡ Zero Tax</h3>
      <p>No hidden fees. Just pure community trading.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>🌍 Community Owned</h3>
      <p>No team dominance. The meme is the leader.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
  <p style="max-width:600px; margin:20px auto; opacity:0.7;">
    FUNCOIN is a meme experiment. It has no intrinsic value and is not financial advice.
    You may lose all your funds. Only participate for fun and entertainment.
  </p>
</div>

<footer>
  © 2026 FUNCOIN. All memes reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
